properties.text: [outlineback=#000000][lineThickness=5] - You have more Orange Pegs set to spawn than there are Pegs in the layout!
[outlineback=#000000][lineThickness=6] Are you sure you're ready to upload your level? Make sure you've done the following:

[outlineback=#000000][lineThickness=6]
- Given your level a name and level description
- Set how many Orange Pegs and Balls on start you want
- Set your background up as you like
- Given your level desired music
- Level meets Content Guidelines

[outlineback=#000000][lineThickness=7]NOTE: PachinGO! has full authority to moderate and delete user created levels if we find such violates our Content Guidelines, which can be found on our website. 
Please behave!

[outlineback=#000000][lineThickness=5] Your custom level is now available for play on the PachinGO! website. 

Thank you for your contribution!

[outlineback=#000000][lineThickness=5] Right click to create a box to highlight and activate Pegs

 Use the Arrows (on-screen or keyboard) to move selected Pegs

 Hold CTRL while moving selected Pegs to move them a single pixel

 Use the Circular Arrows (or the Comma and Period keys) to rotate 
 selected Pegs

 Hold CTRL while rotating selected Pegs to rotate them a single pixel

 Hold Shift when rotating a Peg to rotate it 45 degrees

 Hold CTRL when clicking a Peg to duplicate it

 Press Z to select all Pegs

 Press X to de-select all Pegs
